text: Star Channel is an Australian pay television channel owned by Warner Bros. Discovery EMEA. The channel originally launched as the Australian version of Discovery Home & Health on 7 April 2020. On 1 January 2024, Warner Bros. Discovery EMEA announced that the Australian version of Discovery Home & Health would be rebranded as Star Channel on 1 March 2024. == Logos == file:Discovery H&H.png;|7 April 2020-1 March 2024 file:Star Channel 2023.svg|1 March 2024-present Category:Television channels in Australia
title: Star Channel (Australian TV channel)
